這也可能是第一次約會的（“第三次約會”）

768
00:59:41,344 --> 00:59:44,711
This might be close, these buses are kind of boring.
這個倒還湊合，這些灰狗巴士是挺無聊的

769
00:59:45,982 --> 00:59:53,984
There's a very thin line between simple and clean and powerful,
