01:00:27,290 --> 01:00:31,160
all rules cast aside, no apparent way forward,
所有的規則都被拋棄了，前方看不到出路

780
01:00:31,160 --> 01:00:36,399
that all those designers could perhaps do by the late nineties was to go back
所以這些設計師們在 90 年代末能做的就是回歸

